(18181, 'Eliquis 2.5 mg 20 f.c. tabs.', 'اليكويس 2.5مجم 20 قرص', '406', '532', 'Apixaban', 'Bristol-myers squibb > united company for trading & distribution', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'الوقاية والعلاج من الجلطات', 'Anticoagulant', '2.5 mg', 'Apixaban is indicated for reducing the risk of stroke and systemic embolism in patients who have nonvalvular atrial fibrillation, prophylaxis of deep vein thrombosis(DVT) leading to pulmonary embolism(PE) in patients after a hip or knee replacement surgery, and treatment of DVT and PE to reduce the risk of recurrence[Label,A177565,A6897].', '', '', 5929, '2024-11-09', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(13149, 'Sonidair 0.5 mg/2ml 30 susp. amp. for inh.', 'سونيدير 0.5 مجم/2مل 30 امبول للاستنشاق', '315', '462', 'Budesonide', 'Mdi pharma', 'Susp', 'معلق', '', 'Bronchodilator.anti-inflammatory.glucocorticoid steroid', '0.5 mg', 'Budesonide extended-release capsules are indicated for the treatment and maintenance of mild to moderate Crohn’s disease.[L10601,L10604] Various inhaled budesonide products are indicated for prophylactic therapy in asthma [L10607,L10613,L10619] and to reduce exacerbations of COPD.[L10619] A budesonide nasal spray is available over the counter for symptoms of hay fever and upper respiratory allergies.[L10616] Extended-release capsules are indicated to induce remission of mild to moderate ulcerative colitis[L10622] and a rectal foam is used for mild to moderate distal ulcerative colitis.[L10625] In addition, a delayed-release capsule formulation of budesonide is indicated to reduce proteinuria in adults with IgA nephropathy at risk of rapid disease progression.[L42515,L49540] Budesonide is indicated to treat eosinophilic esophagitis (EoE): For this indication, it is only approved for use in adults in Europe [L42525] while it is approved for short-term use (12 weeks) in patients 11 years of age and older in the US.[L50161]', '6254885221553', '', 920, '2024-06-27', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
